subs.text: Also if you're looking for OPML reading lists to test with, "feedBase" is full of them. That's its purpose. OPML in and out.

Can Trump really kill ObamaCare? Here's a scenario to consider. 1. I have health insurance (thanks to ObamaCare).  2. According to the old rules, my conditions are not pre-existing. 3. In other words, I don't lose my insurance if Repubs kill ObamaCare. 4. It seems Trump's trickery would only apply to people who don't have coverage now.
